	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories TOYS R Us’s much-loved mascot, Geoffrey the Giraffe, treated children to a weekend of fun at South Coast Mall when he made a special appearance. The retailer’s furry mascot walked around handing out balloons and entertaining children, who had the opportunity to capture the moment by having pictures taken and receiving Geoffrey’s autograph, but the excitement was not limited to youngsters, as mall staff took the opportunity to pose with Geoffrey. – Supplied. TOYS R Us’s much-loved mascot, Geoffrey the Giraffe, treated children to a weekend of fun at South Coast Mall when he made a special appearance. The retailer’s furry mascot walked around handing out balloons and entertaining children, who had the opportunity to capture the moment by having pictures taken and receiving Geoffrey’s autograph, but the excitement was not limited to youngsters, as mall staff took the opportunity to pose with Geoffrey. – Supplied. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  